      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CLOSE SHAVE (7) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (18.09) at this track behind Compton Layla in a Other. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Can find winning form. CADILLAC LANDAU (8) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Compton Layla (18.01) in a Other. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Hard to beat again. HENRY BALE (1) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 4th (22.83) at Warrnambool. Has never been out of the money in three starts this course and distance. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Key player if finds best. CADILLAC GIRL (2) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
